The paper deals with visual question answering, which is a task that involves computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also incorporates probabilistic deep learning methods, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with attention maps, which could place it in cs.CL (Computation and Language) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
